ctromagnetic_induction","trap_option":"C","strong_distractors":["B","D"],"why_not_textbook":"Focuses on understanding inductance principles rather than rote memorization or definitions.","why_cuet_level":"Encourages analysis of inductance effects instead of recalling basic terms or concepts directly.","distractor_rationale":{"A":"Correct interpretation of inductance effects based on established principles related to current change opposition.","B":"Incorrectly states that inductance does not depend on physical properties when it actually does influence behavior significantly.","C":"Misrepresents inductance by claiming independence from coil characteristics, which contradicts fundamental electromagnetic principles.","D":"Fails to identify flaws within Statement III regarding dependence on material properties."}}]}
